                     <interp inst="t18191201-154-person1539" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. The tools were pledged with me, but not by the prisoner. The duplicate is mine.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
